8-11 |archive-date=2021-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210726035202/https://www.bjnews.com.cn/detail/162726814414235.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，活跃于[[新浪微博|微博]]，仿照《[[哈扎尔辞典|哈扎尔辞典]]》，自创微博话题“瞎扎尔辞典”<ref>{{Cite web|title=内卷、打工人、凡尔赛：网络流行语还能否勾勒我们的生存？|url=https://xw.qq.com/cmsid/20201214a07cae00?f=newdc|access-date=2021-07-24|author=刘亚光|work=腾讯新闻|publisher=新京报|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724041149/https://xw.qq.com/cmsid/20201214a07cae00?f=newdc|dead-url=no}}</ref>，经常发文暗讽[[中国政府|中国政府]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=疫情期間「篤灰病毒」同告爆發 社科院教師武漢教授同遭舉報|url=https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/sack-02102020081343.html|access-date=2021-07-21|work=Radio Free Asia|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210723053429/https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/sack-02102020081343.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾遭学生举报<ref>{{Cite news|title=李文亮事件後續：更多「吹哨人」遭中國當局打壓|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51463097|newspaper=BBC News 中文|accessdate=2021-07-21|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724135013/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51463097|dead-url=no}}</ref>。米果文化内容总监，<ref>{{cite web |title=周玄毅 |url=http://philosophy.whu.edu.cn/info/1185/7295.htm |website=武汉大学哲学学院 |access-date=2021-02-03 |archive-date=2020-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620124719/http://philosophy.whu.edu.cn/info/1185/7295.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>曾参与创作《好好说话》《小学问》等系列网络知识脱口秀节目。<ref>{{cite web |author1=万建辉 |title=武大辩论“名嘴”周玄毅妙解90后的“人生焦虑” |url=http://www.cjrbapp.cjn.cn/p/17769.html |website=长江日报}}</ref>

